channel.title: ServerStatus Page Not Working Successfully For Me
channel.description:
EDIT: Just noticed my IP changed last night, found out what the problem was, a moderator can lock this thread now.)
Hello, I have turned my server online and tried to send in a request to the server status page.
However after I send it in it says that my server is offline, but it is definitely online.
Could I please get some help? I don't know what is going on.
